name: Paw Puppy Gift Share Mission
description:
Paw Puppy Gift Share Mission is so simple and funny game . Easy to play, but hard to master and get high scores. Also, This game will bring you amazing and great experiences , beside your family. This game is a world of music, autos, trees, street, impediments, gift, reindeer and prettiest puppies in the warm air of The city.

You will incarnate in the prettiest puppy who rides the car on the Cities street with the mission of giving gifts to his friends. The prettiest puppy and car can turn left, turn right and jump up to pass the impediments. On his way, there are many prettiest puppies who are waiting for gifts.
